## Review Section

### What Was Fixed ✅

**Issue:** Clicking "Edit" or "Delete" buttons in card menu triggered both the menu action AND the card detail panel to open.

**Root Cause:** Menu items didn't have `e.stopPropagation()`, so click events bubbled up to the parent div in KanbanColumn which has `onClick={onCardClick}`.

**Solution:** Added `e.stopPropagation()` to both "Edit" and "Delete" button handlers in KanbanCard.tsx (lines 195-208).

### Files Modified

| File | Lines Changed | Description |
|------|--------------|-------------|
| `src/widgets/Kanban/KanbanCard.tsx` | 195-208 | Added stopPropagation to menu buttons |
